
Users
-----
Auth Token (Unique)
Phone Number (Unique)
UUID (Unique)
Public Key
Private Key -- *requires password on key

Verifications
-------------
Phone Number
Confirmation Token

Location
--------
User ID
TimeStamp
Encrpyted Location
Verification Hash

Publish:
  UUID, Timestamp, Verification


rails g model user auth_token:string:uniq phone_number:string:uniq uuid:string:uniq public_key:text private_key:text
rails g model verification phone_number:string confirmation_token:string

rails g model location user_id:integer encrypted:string verification:string timestamps

